# Original-form capture produces large binaries (WARC, HTML, PDF, PNG, video).
# Per CAPTURE-RUNBOOK.md, these are kept in off-platform custody (which doubles
# as the manifest's required "second custodian"); only the small integrity record
# is tracked in-repo so the custody chain is auditable without committing GBs.
*/original/*
!*/original/manifest.json
!*/original/sha256sums.txt
!*/original/archive-org-snapshots.txt
